    "subject": "「纯真的歌谣」：《原神》稻妻篇OST2雾海纪行主题印象曲MV",
    "content": "<p><br></p><div class=\"ql-image\"><div class=\"ql-image-wrp\"><img src=\"https://upload-os-bbs.hoyolab.com/upload/2022/04/11/1015373/01169216cf0cae61a40bdb0b357b9224_7828094389659260187.jpg\"></div></div><p>「纯真的歌谣」Song of Innocence</p><p>由上海乐团乐手与合唱团小朋友们录制，海南乐团乐手与小朋友们演绎，共同呈现《原神》稻妻雾海纪行主题印象曲——「纯真的歌谣」Song of Innocence。</p><p>《原神》第二张稻妻篇OST《佚落迁忘之岛 Islands of the Lost and Forgotten》将于4月13日上线。</p><p>作曲：陈致逸</p><p>指挥：齐放</p><p>合唱录制：上海Sfuture艺术团</p><p>竖琴录制：权宁枚</p><p>弦乐录制：龙之艺交响乐团</p><p>合唱表演：紫贝合唱团</p><p>弦乐表演：三亚爱乐乐团</p><p>出品：HOYO-MiX</p><p><br></p><p>曲目信息：</p><p>纯真的歌谣 Song of Innocence</p><p>作曲：Yu-Peng Chen 陈致逸</p><p>指挥：Fang Qi 齐放</p><p>合唱：Sfuture Art Group Sfuture艺术团</p><p>竖琴：Ningmei Quan 权宁枚</p><p>乐队：Art of Dragon Orchestra 龙之艺交响乐团</p><p>录音棚：Shanghai Media Group 上海广播大厦</p><p>录音师：Jiawei Mo 莫家伟</p><p>混音师：Zach Huang 黄巍</p><p>出品：HOYO-MiX</p><div class=\"mhy-video-frame ql-frame\"><iframe border=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" framespacing=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/O_Udh58C2dM\"></iframe></div><p><br></p>",
    "article_url": "https://www.hoyolab.com/article/4227869"
  },
