    "subject": "《原神》佚落迁忘之岛 Islands of the Lost and Forgotten",
    "content": "<p><br></p><div class=\"ql-image\"><div class=\"ql-image-wrp\"><img src=\"https://upload-os-bbs.hoyolab.com/upload/2022/04/12/1015373/d7f0832dfcf87d9df9cee1ac079464b3_6498522108045326028.jpg\"></div></div><p>《原神》第二张稻妻篇OST《佚落迁忘之岛 Islands of the Lost and Forgotten》正式上线，专辑分为《遗忘与冥思的岛屿 Isles of Serenity and Amnesia》、《海渊之下 Beneath the Abyssal Depth》与《稻妻征战记2 Battles of Inazuma 2》3张分碟，共收录60首由HOYO-MiX音乐团队为《原神》稻妻地区创作的原声音乐，部分音乐与Sony Music Entertainment (Japan) Inc.联合制作。</p><p><br></p><p>特别感谢日本方合作伙伴:</p><p>（以下署名采用日语书写方式，鸣谢顺序不分先后）</p><p>Assistant Producer 制作助理:Tomonori Hirata (Sony Music Publishing (Japan) Inc.) 平田 有了</p><p>Musician Contractor 乐手承包人: Tsutomu Satomi (SHANGRI-LA Inc.) 里見 勉、Aki Haruyama (SHANGRI-LA Inc.) 春山 あき</p><p>Coordinator 音乐协助: Ma Xuetong (Sony Group Corporation) 馬 雪潼、Tomoki Murata (Sony Music Entertainment (Japan) Inc.) 村田 知樹、Ryu Haku (Sony Music Entertainment (Japan) Inc.) 劉 博</p><p>Music Business Affairs商务合作: Kana Tsuji (Sony Music Publishing (Japan) Inc.) 辻 佳奈、Ichiro Murakami (Sony Music Publishing (Japan) Inc.) 村上 伊知郎</p><p>Recording Assistants 录音助理: Ryuho Ichikawa (Joint1) 市川 竜帆、Ayumu Musha (Joint1) 武舎 歩、Kenta Murakami (Onkio Haus) 村上 健太</p><p>Special Thanks 鸣谢: Yi Fengyu 伊豊宇、Sumiyo Takahashi (Joint1) 髙橋 純、Yohei Horiuchi (Joint1) 堀内 陽平</p><div class=\"mhy-video-frame ql-frame\"><iframe border=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" framespacing=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/S2q7r4_UaYM\"></iframe></div><div class=\"mhy-video-frame ql-frame\"><iframe border=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" framespacing=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/skI5KmOIHl4\"></iframe></div><div class=\"mhy-video-frame ql-frame\"><iframe border=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" framespacing=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QrSeAOUZpeQ\"></iframe></div><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 146, 1);\">点击此处收听《佚落迁忘之岛 Islands of the Lost and Forgotten》</strong></p><p><a href=\"http://open.spotify.com/album/2rdPLD1XUQ6iN1KeQ0wrzu\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Spotify</strong></a></p><p><a href=\"https://music.apple.com/us/album/1618475874\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>iTunes/Apple Music</strong></a></p>",
