    "subject": "「流风眷堇庭」2.6版本活动速递第二期",
    "content": "<p><br></p><div class=\"ql-image\"><div class=\"ql-image-wrp\"><img src=\"https://upload-os-bbs.hoyolab.com/upload/2022/04/13/1015373/16fb9bcf624424cf15be1b3504204448_7690665806395416816.png\"></div></div><p>近期又将开启不少全新活动，一起往下看看吧~</p><div class=\"ql-image\"><div class=\"ql-image-wrp\"><img src=\"https://upload-os-bbs.hoyolab.com/upload/2022/04/13/1015373/64a1fd0dcaaa78f3c42b2bb9773ed1fa_7195816053225196667.jpg\"></div></div><p><br></p>",
