    "subject": "《原神》剧情PV-「歌仙逸话」",
    "content": "<p><br></p><div class=\"ql-image\"><div class=\"ql-image-wrp\"><img src=\"https://upload-os-bbs.hoyolab.com/upload/2022/04/13/1015373/0d65357a90e380658229c46badad6f42_6526570985071396925.jpg\"></div></div><p>昔时，稻妻有能诗者五人，留歌仙逸闻。几经曲折，风波伏定。</p><p>今日，堇庭亦现才佳者五位，探荣采疑事。水落石出，重书旧话</p><div class=\"mhy-video-frame ql-frame\"><iframe border=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" framespacing=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/oYE_9lq-IOo\"></iframe></div><p><br></p>",
