    "subject": "《原神》PV短片——「雪霁逢椿」",
    "content": "<p><br></p><div class=\"ql-image\"><div class=\"ql-image-wrp\"><img src=\"https://upload-os-bbs.hoyolab.com/upload/2022/04/18/1015373/d9c82a912b1dbb8265ae740f3c152e8a_3362798640524294141.jpg\"></div></div><p>花开再艳，也终有一日须经受严冬的考验。</p><p>但霜雪总有停时，寒木依然挺立。</p><p>待云开雪霁，方觉春日已至。</p><div class=\"mhy-video-frame ql-frame\"><iframe border=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" framespacing=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/v_QkcrKZ-Wc\"></iframe></div><p><br></p>",
